<h4><u><br />What factors should I consider in deciding to retake a prerequisite class?</u></h4>
<p>
    Please consider the following:<br />
    <ul>
        <li>Any repeated prerequisite courses will be discounted by .3 (e.g. A to A-) in the application process.</li>
        <li>
            If a prerequisite course is retaken, the most recent grade is the one considered during the application process. Thus, it is
            important that you improve your grade the second time you take the class.
        </li>
        <li>Premanagement courses may be repeated only once.</li>
    </ul>
</p>

